HEADWORD: Octogild
<hw>Oc"to*gild</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Octo-</ets> +
AS. <ets>gild</ets> payment.]</ety> <fld>(Anglo-Saxon Law)</fld> <def>A
pecuniary compensation for an injury, of eight times the value of the
thing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

